  "bio25": "Lucius P. Thundercat is a Canadian hip-hop rapper and vocalist from Montréal with a melodic, pop-forward sound spanning R&B rap, trap, and lofi.",
  "bio100": "Lucius P. Thundercat is a Canadian hip-hop rapper and vocalist based in Montréal, releasing through Silk Velvet Records. His sound is melodic and pop-forward — R&B-influenced rap that moves through trap and lofi, touching boom bap as texture. He works feature-first: signature collaborations include \"Must Be Love\" with Magi Merlin. Active since 2014, his catalog is available across all major streaming platforms and Bandcamp.",
